            <div type="transcript" id="J997">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Crumbling is not an instant's Act</l>
                    <l>A fundamental pause</l>
                    <l>Delapidation's processes</l>
                    <l>Are organized Decays.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>'Tis first a Cobweb on the Soul</l>
                    <l>A Cuticle of Dust</l>
                    <l>A Borer in the Axis</l>
                    <l>An Elemental Rust --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Ruin is formal -- Devils work</l>
                    <l>Consecutive and slow --</l>
                    <l>Fail in an instant, no man did</l>
                    <l>Slipping -- is Crashe's law.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
